We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the revised policy on this page with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.

